-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2377748%2F0616_1024.jpeg&h=042642fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落井下石，OT可以有10皮既黑警<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEVVuPe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEVVuPe.png&h=ee3c57ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比橡膠子彈爆頭既示威者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28mLDhh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28mLDhh.png&h=26aadb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拔萃女教師爆眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2370000/2374902/2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2370000%2F2374902%2F2_1024.jpg&h=672cfccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他太多太多，不能盡錄<br />\n<img src=\"http://www2.iso2.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/%E6%8B%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%8B%E8%85%95%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.iso2.cc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F%25E6%258B%2597%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F.jpg&h=7e2204d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/16/uvf0jk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2Fuvf0jk.png&h=ae92f3da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n你仲割唔割？<br />\n仲想唔想互屌？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔完美，可以檢討，但唔好互屌同白白分化，<br />\n諗下五大訴求，望下呢堆圖 警惕自己，<br />\n同路人點樣錯，點樣用武力，都唔夠對家萬份之一"},{"pid":"5305915dded3cebbe38fb2d62b52e284829a4e8a","tid":1799940,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" clas